50|$|Killyloch is a {{malt whisky}} which was {{distilled}} at the Glenflagler <b>Malt</b> <b>Distillery</b> and was first distilled and bonded in February 1965. Glenflagler <b>Malt</b> <b>Distillery</b> was a historic “Lowland” <b>malt</b> <b>distillery</b> and {{was closed and}} demolished by Inver House Distillers Limited in July 1985.|$|E
