50|$|House of Hazelwood is a {{brand of}} art deco-inspired blended Scotch whisky, owned and {{produced}} by William Grant & Sons. The whisky is made with spirit produced at Girvan grain distillery, Kininvie <b>malt</b> <b>distillery</b> and spirit from the Grant family's private collection.|$|E
